<div class="container">
    <h2>Welcome, <%= @user.full_name %>, to your very own Bandroid user profile page!</h2><hr>

      <% if @user.musician %>

        <% if @user.musician.stage_name.empty? == false %>

          <h3>Hey <%= @user.musician.stage_name %>, you crazy rock star! Feel free to click through to your <%= link_to "Musician profile page", @user.musician %>, where you can do stuff like edit your details (which are as follows for now):
                <ul>
                <% if @user.musician.stage_name.empty? == false %>
                  <li>Stage Name: <%= @user.musician.stage_name %></li>
                <% else %>
                  <li>No Stage Name</li>
                <% end %>

                  <li>Location: <%= @user.musician.location %> </li>
                  <li>Bio: <%= @user.musician.bio %> </li>
                  <li>Instruments:
                    <ul>
                      <% @user.musician.instruments.each do |instrument| %>
                      <li> <%= instrument.name %> </li>
                      <% end %>
                    </ul></li>
                  <li>Bands:
                    <% if @user.musician.bands.empty? == false %>
                      <ul>
                        <% @user.musician.bands.each do |band| %>
                        <li> <%= link_to band.name, band %> </li>
                        <% end %>
                      </ul></li>
                    <% else %>
                      <ul>
                        <li>None yet.... Why not <%= link_to "start a new band", new_band_path %> right now? No time like the present!</li>
                      </ul>
                    <% end %>
                </ul>
          </h3><br><br>

        <% else %>

          <h3> Is "<%= @user.full_name %>" a little too formal for your tastes?<br><br>

          No problem, just click through to your <%= link_to "Musician profile page", @user.musician %>, where you can edit your profile to include a Stage Name.</h3><br>

        <% end %>

      <% else %>

        <h3> Is "<%= @user.full_name %>" a little too formal for your tastes?<br><br>

        Well, not to worry; once you create your Musician profile, you can give yourself a Stage Name, which can be anything you like really (even *shock horror* keeping your ditchwater-dull real name!).<br><br>

        Where do I create my Musician profile, I hear you asking? Do it <%= link_to "HERE", new_musician_path %>, innit.</h3>

      <% end %><hr>



    Alternatively, click <%= link_to 'here', '/musicians' %> for a list of all your fellow musicians, while in <%= link_to 'this other place', '/bands' %> is a list of all the bands on Bandroid. Awesome.<br><br>  
  </div>
